    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the spaghetti is cooking, wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Chop your <strong>baby plum tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Combine <strong>half </strong>the <strong>lemon zest</strong> (save the rest for later!) with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>in a large bowl with your <strong>honey</strong> and the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> lemon honey dressing</strong></p>",
