    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, the <strong>remaining lemon zest</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>pepper </strong>and mix it all together</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
